        "description": "Displays custom text on the LED name badge. You can include predefined icons in your text using the format `:icon_name:` (e.g., `:star:`, `:heart:`).\n\n### Request Body\n- `text` (string): The text to display on the LED badge. Can include icon placeholders.\n\n### Response\n- `status` (string): Confirmation message\n- `text` (string): The text that was displayed\n\n### Example\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"Hello World! :star:\"\n}\n```\n\n### Success Response (200)\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"Text displayed on LED\",\n  \"text\": \"Hello World! :star:\"\n}\n```"
