        "description": "Retrieves a list of all available predefined icons that can be used in the LED badge text. Icons are returned in the format `:icon_name:` and can be embedded directly in the text parameter of the `/display-text` endpoint.\n\n### Response\n- `icons` (array): List of available icon names in the format `:icon_name:`\n\n### Success Response (200)\n```json\n{\n  \"icons\": [\n    \":star:\",\n    \":heart:\",\n    \":smile:\",\n    \":arrow:\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Usage\nUse the returned icon names in your text when calling the `/display-text` endpoint. For example:\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"Welcome :star: :heart:\"\n}\n```"
